{
  "id": "adv_main_01_08_05",
  "title": "星見編2章30話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-cmn001.m4a",
      "text": "未公開映像！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unreleased footage?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。実は{user}さんの所で\n麻奈ちゃんの映像を観せてもらってたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You see‚ I’ve been visiting {user}\nso he could show me unreleased footage of Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.810861682891845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "だったらお付き合いのことは\nはっきり否定してくれればよかったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why didn’t you just deny it\nwhen we asked if you were dating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.767208113814846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、絶対に秘密だぞって\n{user}さんが言うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because {user} made me promise\nto keep it a secret.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.828253904978432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "とんでもない誤解をされているようだったから\n正直に話そうと思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And since the misunderstandings blew way out of control‚\nI thought we should be honest with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.478643599423506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰にも見せるつもりはない映像だったんだけど\n芽衣に偶然見つけられちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn’t planning on showing that footage to anyone‚\nbut Mei found it by accident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.69791390101117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "偶然ってどうやって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By accident? How could she—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4312472343445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それはどこですの！？\nあのオンボロ小屋に行けばいいんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where is this footage?!\nWill we find it if we go to that rundown shed?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.00106583436333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いてくれ。持ってきてあるからみんなで観よう\n長瀬麻奈の……世界に一つしかない、貴重な映像だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down. I’ll bring it over and we can all watch it together.\nIt’s very special‚ one-of-a-kind footage of Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.73439916769667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "世界に一つしかない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One of a kind…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.75045325756077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（要はテレビ未公開VTRや星見プロで撮った映像だ）\n（俺の小屋にあったのは本当だし、偶然じゃない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’m talking about a collection of footage never aired on TV and films shot by Hoshimi Productions.)\n(It’s true that I had this footage in my shed. It’s not a coincidence.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.93056667645776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 55.56390000979109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ふぉおおおおっ！　楽屋の麻奈様！　麻奈様っ！\nあぁんっ！　レアですわ！　お宝ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!!! Goddess Mana in the dressing room! Goddess Mana!\nAww! What a rarity! What a treasure!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.46390000979112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "なんかこういう舞台裏からの映像っていうのも\nまた違ったライブ感があっていいですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Footage filmed from the wings backstage\nhas its own unique concert feel. I really like it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.27970287315249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "最高ですわ！　女神ですわ！\nなんでこれを私に隠していましたの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Simply perfect! My Goddess!\nWhy did you hide this from me?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.94636953981916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、未公開映像だし\n亡くなった方のプライベートでもあるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s private‚ for one thing.\nWe have to honor the privacy of the deceased‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.81303620648583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ステージに向かう麻奈さん……\n……すごく、いい表情ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana is about to go on stage…\nWhat a great look in her eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.74636953981916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.36488810425533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.40023961907161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁっ……！　あぁん……！　あっ、あっ……！\nちょっと！　カメラワーク悪いですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! Ohh! Ah! Ah!\nHey! What shoddy camera work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.16690628573828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、もっと静かに観ませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ could you watch it a little more quietly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4443714702679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、すずちゃんってば\nホントに麻奈さんのこと……あ、そういうことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heheh‚ oh‚ Suzu.\nYou really do love Mana… Oh‚ now I get it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3599269791994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、渚",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s up‚ Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.48639762914304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "小屋で、芽衣ちゃんの……その\nちょっとエッチな声が聞こえたでしょ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we heard Mei in the shed‚ you know‚\nwhen she was moaning‚ remember?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.42696452653531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええ……。「もう一回」とか\n……って、な、何を言わせるのよ、もう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right… When she said‚ “one more time.”\nHey! Don’t make me say that. Jeez.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6602978598687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁんっ！　アンコールですわ！　アンコール！\nもう一回今のところを再生してもいいですわよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohh! Encore! I demand an encore!\nOne more time! Let me see that one more time‚ okay?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7936311932021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほどね。じゃあ、その……ヘンな声も\n今のすずみたいに興奮して……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I get it. So‚ when she‚ uh‚ made that weird moaning voice‚\nwas she just excited like Suzu is right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.91392114778844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "そう、じゃないのかな？\n良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think so?\nWhat a relief…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.91392114778836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まだ一つ疑問があるんだけど\n……芽衣",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there’s still one thing that doesn’t add up.\nMei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9472544811217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "んー、何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.26211616019884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はどうして急に\nお姉ちゃんのことを気にし出したの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did you suddenly\ntake an interest in my sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3954495173741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
